%% Diagram: Sorting Hat request routing
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client
    participant LB as nginx + OpenResty
    participant SH as Sorting Hat (Lua)
    participant CP as Routing control plane
    participant APP as Shared app workers
    participant POD as Pod (MySQL + Redis + Memcached)

    Client->>LB: HTTPS request to shop domain
    LB->>SH: Hand off request
    SH->>CP: Lookup pod by host / domain
    CP-->>SH: pod_id
    SH->>SH: Inject X-Sorting-Hat-PodId header
    SH->>APP: Forward request
    APP->>APP: Read pod header, pick connection pool
    APP->>POD: SQL / cache calls scoped to shop_id
    POD-->>APP: Response
    APP-->>Client: HTTP response
